JAVASCRIPT

A Programming Language invented in the year 1995 by Bredan Eitch.

Netscape with the help of Sun Microsystems came with the Language JavaScript.

The basic objective of JS is to make the WEBSITE interactive.

It is a Client-Side Scripting Language.

The period before JS people were using only HyperLinks to navigate from one page to another.

It is more powerful that it can be used in web, mobile and desktop applications.

It can also be used for game development.

90% of all the companies use JavaScript for frontend.

JavaScript's trademark is owned by ORACLE.

Every browser has an inbuilt JavaScript Engine to work.


